                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-heart"></span>
                    <h4>Care</h4>
                    <p>Our producers grow vegetables with their love </p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-lock"></span>
                    <h4>JOB DONE</h4>
                    <p>Best delivery in town</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <br><br>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-leaf"></span>
                    <h4>GREEN</h4>
                    <p>All we have are eco products</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-certificate"></span>
                    <h4>CERTIFIED</h4>
                    <p>European standards in an european country</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-sm-4">
                    <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-wrench"></span>
                    <h4>HARD WORK</h4>
                    <p>Hard work so that you'll enjoy healthy food</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>



        <hr />



